1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 26=

3
00:00:18,037 --> 00:00:21,937
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

4
00:00:22,050 --> 00:00:25,575
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

5
00:00:26,137 --> 00:00:30,187
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

6
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:32,640
Are you here to bid me farewell?

7
00:00:35,359 --> 00:00:36,679
I'm here to return what's yours.

8
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,200
What?

9
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,039
Will you arrest me?

10
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:49,925
♪To the moment we first met♪

11
00:00:50,479 --> 00:00:51,840
If you don't arrest me now,

12
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,439
you'll lose the chance forever.

13
00:00:58,237 --> 00:01:02,212
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

14
00:01:02,350 --> 00:01:05,937
♪I end up creating another knot instead♪

15
00:01:06,175 --> 00:01:10,187
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

16
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:12,480
Take it.

17
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,480
Leave.

18
00:01:18,237 --> 00:01:25,837
♪To the moment we first met♪

19
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,920
You're letting me go.

20
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,640
Then, why give this pendant back to me?

21
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,680
What I gave to you

22
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,719
will always belong to you.

23
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,120
How sweet those words sound.

24
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,159
I don't understand.

25
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:46,719
Since you knew my identity all along,

26
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,959
why did you insist on staying with me?

27
00:01:53,137 --> 00:01:53,536
I...

28
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,719
You knew all along

29
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:56,359
that we could never be together.

30
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,120
So why get engaged to me?

31
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,480
Why plan a wedding?

32
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,719
Were you planning to apprehend me?

33
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,480
I was not.

34
00:02:05,937 --> 00:02:09,525
♪To the moment we first met♪

35
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,879
I can't say.

36
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,919
Then, let me ask you one last thing.

37
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,120
Were your feelings for me

38
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,879
ever real?

39
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:23,759
Of course.

40
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:28,590
Why didn't you have the courage
to face this with me?

41
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,039
Chang.

42
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,400
Let me ask you a question in return.

43
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,120
You've been deceiving me
by design since the start.

44
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,360
Were your feelings for me real?

45
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:41,872
♪We move on to where it all began♪

46
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:46,599
I love you because you are Mao Buyu.

47
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,599
It has nothing to do

48
00:02:49,810 --> 00:02:51,120
with who you are or what you do.

49
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,639
I lied to you

50
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,000
only because I didn't want to lose you.

51
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,039
Buyu.

52
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,719
Have you ever once

53
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,599
heard of the Jade Squirrel
harming a soul?

54
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,240
I have never hurt
a single person in my entire life.

55
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,280
My only mistake

56
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,560
was falling in love with you.

57
00:03:26,287 --> 00:03:30,250
♪We move on to where it all began♪

58
00:03:30,250 --> 00:03:34,100
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

59
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:36,525
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

60
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,360
I thought you would protect me forever.

61
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:43,280
I didn't realize you didn't care at all.

62
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:52,879
Chang.

63
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:54,400
Chang!

64
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:56,840
Chang!

65
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,560
It's not how you think it is.

66
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:02,280
You're letting them arrest me.

67
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,400
Have you protected me in any way?

68
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,199
I am a constable.

69
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,800
How am I supposed to protect you?

70
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,719
You should at least know
right from wrong.

71
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,520
If you were arrested on false charges,

72
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,839
I would use every legal means
to get you out.

73
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:22,720
I suppose I should thank you then,

74
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,560
Constable Mao.

75
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:27,800
Buyu.

76
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,560
We need to talk...

77
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,120
Chu Yunchang!

78
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:35,800
Sir.

79
00:04:36,490 --> 00:04:37,560
You dare to show your face?

80
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,759
I'm bringing you in now!

81
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:39,879
Father! Father!

82
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,199
Chu Yunchang, haven't you brought
enough ruin upon my family?

83
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,800
Why won't you just let my son go?

84
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,800
And do you plan to let me go?

85
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,560
Enough talk!

86
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,820
Come with me to the authorities.

87
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:53,480
Sir, if I truly wanted to leave,

88
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,240
no one here could stop me.

89
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,199
I'll take you down now!

90
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:56,519
Father!

91
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:57,290
Get out of the way!

92
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,720
Father!

93
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,439
Move!

94
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,120
Go, hurry!

95
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,600
Father! Father!

96
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,439
Are you even a constable anymore?

97
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,120
Father, no!

98
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,079
Stop!

99
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:15,480
Buyu.

100
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:16,480
Father-in-law.

101
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:17,959
Perfect timing.

102
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,480
Help me catch the Jade Squirrel!

103
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:19,959
Father,

104
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,240
just give Yunchang a break.

105
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:21,879
Father-in-law,

106
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:22,720
no need to pursue her.

107
00:05:22,730 --> 00:05:23,990
With Yunchang's lightness skill,

108
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,040
no one can catch her
if she wants to disappear.

109
00:05:26,362 --> 00:05:26,887
(Master Constable)

110
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,079
You both call yourselves constables,

111
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:32,920
yet you stood by
and watched a criminal escape?

112
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,399
You are a disgrace to the Mao name!

113
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,160
Father,

114
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:37,040
Buyu and Yunchang were engaged.

115
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,720
Asking him to arrest her

116
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,319
is impossible for him.

117
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:41,879
He's been bewitched by that vixen!

118
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,260
I'm making him come to his senses!

119
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,600
Chang is not a vixen.

120
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,839
You're still defending her?

121
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,399
Father-in-law,

122
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,360
calm down.

123
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:50,959
Buyu actually had good intentions

124
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,000
when he let her go.

125
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,079
What good intentions?

126
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,240
If Chu Yunchang were caught here
at our house,

127
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,839
wouldn't that invite gossip?

128
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:00,680
People would say we're in league
with the Sacred Hand Sect.

129
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,759
By letting her leave,

130
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,120
she can be caught elsewhere.

131
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:07,680
Only then can we distance
our families from one another.

132
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,150
Well, if you put it that way,

133
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,759
it does make some sense.

134
00:06:30,850 --> 00:06:33,762
(Meditation Hall)

135
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,920
Brother, stop drinking.

136
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:40,360
You just got back
and you're already at it again.

137
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,399
I'm fine.

138
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,000
Father, you're back.

139
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,040
What's going on?

140
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,759
Chang.

141
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,160
Do you have any idea?

142
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,879
That pure gold Sacred Token

143
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:04,839
has been causing us so much trouble.

144
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:07,839
Can you guess
where it's been all this time?

145
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,240
Actually,

146
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,839
it's been inside
the Gate Bureau the whole time.

147
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,720
How did you find out?

148
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,800
Lately,

149
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,959
I've been conducting
a secret investigation.

150
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,959
I discovered that

151
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,225
back when the Four Thief Kings

152
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:39,360
stole the Sacred Token together,

153
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:42,279
they agreed to meet
at the Yanyu Pavilion in Suzhou.

154
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,839
(Token)
(But that day...)

155
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,800
- Cheers!
- Come on, drink!

156
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,839
(Everything went wrong.)

157
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,680
(The exact reason for their falling out)

158
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,759
(remains a mystery.)

159
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:56,480
The gold Sacred Token
reportedly vanished,

160
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,519
while the other Sacred Token

161
00:07:58,839 --> 00:08:00,759
stayed in Dongfang Qing's possession.

162
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:03,000
Then, seemingly overnight,

163
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:06,399
the Imperial Court turned
against the sects.

164
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,879
Many were branded as cults,

165
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,680
then banned and eradicated.

166
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,240
Dongfang Qing knew

167
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:17,519
this was all because
they stole the Sacred Token.

168
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,240
It triggered chaos in the Martial World

169
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:23,360
and destroyed
the Imperial Court's trust in them.

170
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:24,920
And since

171
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:28,319
he was the one primarily responsible,

172
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,519
he was despised
by both sides of the law.

173
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,625
By then, that Sacred Token

174
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,960
had clearly become a hot potato.

175
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,960
He didn't dare show it ever again.

176
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:41,960
So he lived
as a fugitive under a false name.

177
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:45,679
Unfortunately, with Dongfang Qing dead,

178
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,639
the truth has gone
to the grave with him.

179
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,360
I've discovered

180
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:57,720
that Dongfang Qing has a twin brother

181
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,720
named Dongfang Bai.

182
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,919
Dongfang Qing has a brother?

183
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,120
They may be twins,

184
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,360
but their personalities
are polar opposites.

185
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:12,480
While Dongfang Bai was also a thief,

186
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:14,080
he wasn't a cat burglar.

187
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,600
He was a mild-mannered man

188
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,600
who disliked trouble.

189
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,519
He usually just stayed home,

190
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,600
making tools
for people in the Martial World.

191
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:26,840
Dongfang Qing was hell-bent on

192
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:29,759
making an enemy of the Sacred Hand Sect.

193
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:32,120
To stay out of it, Dongfang Bai fled

194
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,840
to Xichuan under an alias.

195
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:38,039
Word is he's living under the protection

196
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,679
of the Shen family.

197
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,679
As of now,

198
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:44,879
he should still be alive.

199
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,639
How can you be so sure?

200
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,320
Do you both remember Shen Yidie?

201
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,159
Before Shen Yidie left back then,

202
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:58,200
she once tried
to claim Dongfang Qing's body.

203
00:09:58,799 --> 00:09:59,720
I caught her in the act.

204
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:03,039
She claimed
she was doing it for a friend.

205
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:07,639
Does that mean Dongfang Bai
is hiding with the Shen family?

206
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:11,080
But Shen Gongquan
is the Grandmaster of Xichuan.

207
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:13,960
Why would he have any history
with Dongfang Qing

208
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,879
from the South?

209
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:17,320
Aside from his brother Dongfang Bai,

210
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,320
it couldn't be anyone else.

211
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,759
Then, how did you find out

212
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,960
the gold Sacred Token
was in the Gate Bureau?

213
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,120
(That old fox...)

214
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,879
(He even kept
his own granddaughter in the dark.)

215
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,240
After a long and winding journey,

216
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,840
it has finally returned to my hands.

217
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,360
(Token)

218
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,360
Because I discovered

219
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,919
the man behind Dongfang Qing

220
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,559
was Luo Shixun.

221
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,639
No wonder I found no trace of it

222
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,759
despite searching for all these years.

223
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:26,879
It turns out that

224
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:29,799
it was always in the Gate Bureau.

225
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,360
So all these years,

226
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:33,639
the Court's suppression of our sects

227
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,559
was all Luo Shixun's doing.

228
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,639
I wouldn't rule that out.

229
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,399
Now that he has both Sacred Tokens,

230
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,279
I wonder what his next move will be.

231
00:11:45,237 --> 00:11:46,436
This is quite a predicament.

232
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:49,080
I'll have to investigate further.

233
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,200
Commissioner.

234
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,000
Mao Jixian, welcome.

235
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,240
Take a seat.

236
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:04,080
Greetings, Commissioner.

237
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:07,600
There's no need
for such formalities between us.

238
00:12:10,780 --> 00:12:11,559
What's on your mind?

239
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,519
My son, Buyu,

240
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:17,750
was deceived by Chu Yunchang
of the Sacred Hand Sect.

241
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:21,200
But my son is innocent.

242
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:23,679
I beg you to clear his name.

243
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,759
It's not like I've punished him.

244
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,039
I ask that you step in

245
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,639
and clarify the matter for him.

246
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,440
Jixian,

247
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,080
seeing as we aren't exactly family,

248
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:44,039
it's hard for me to speak up for Buyu.

249
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:48,360
I wish to propose a marriage
for my son Buyu

250
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:51,559
to your granddaughter, Ms. Wushuang.

251
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:57,840
There is no need for that.

252
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,440
I hope you can give them your blessing.

253
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:01,279
Very well.

254
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:03,159
Wushuang has always been fond of Buyu.

255
00:13:03,759 --> 00:13:04,840
I wouldn't oppose it.

256
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,840
However,

257
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:10,960
we still need to see
how Buyu feels about it.

258
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,879
Marriage has always been

259
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,879
a matter of the parents' orders.

260
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:17,039
As his father, I will decide for him.

261
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:18,080
He won't dare to refuse.

262
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,120
Good.

263
00:13:19,519 --> 00:13:22,360
Have Buyu propose to Wushuang himself.

264
00:13:22,737 --> 00:13:26,279
You want him to propose in person?

265
00:13:26,625 --> 00:13:27,265
But...

266
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:31,240
Buyu turned Wushuang down that day.

267
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,679
Buyu must propose in person

268
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,399
so that Wushuang's dignity

269
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:36,519
can be truly restored.

270
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,440
As long as Buyu proposes to Wushuang,

271
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,960
I will put in a good word for him.

272
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,080
Yes, sir.

273
00:14:09,675 --> 00:14:11,287
(Li Wen, Vice Minister of Justice,
From Yangling)

274
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,440
Master Mao.

275
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,639
Sanhuai, you're here.

276
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,720
Jixian,

277
00:14:22,879 --> 00:14:24,840
you shouldn't be looking at this.

278
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,440
My apologies. I was out of line.

279
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:31,600
Do you need something from me, Jixian?

280
00:14:32,879 --> 00:14:35,240
I have a favor to ask.

281
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:38,120
Why use the word "favor" between us?

282
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,399
Speak your mind.

283
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:44,440
It's about my son Buyu

284
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,360
and Wushuang.

285
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,600
I thought as much.

286
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,600
Sanhuai,

287
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:56,840
please help me talk some sense
into my stubborn son.

288
00:14:59,559 --> 00:15:00,639
Rest assured, Jixian.

289
00:15:00,879 --> 00:15:03,120
You can leave this matter to me.

290
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,720
My thanks, Sanhuai.

291
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,000
Take care now.

292
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,559
Thank you.

293
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:12,320
Enjoy.

294
00:15:15,559 --> 00:15:16,320
Buyu,

295
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:19,240
your father came to see me
two nights ago.

296
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:20,759
My father?

297
00:15:20,759 --> 00:15:21,399
Indeed.

298
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,039
What did he want?

299
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:25,440
It was about you, naturally.

300
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:26,600
Me?

301
00:15:29,159 --> 00:15:32,240
He wasn't asking you
to fix the merit records, was he?

302
00:15:36,639 --> 00:15:38,600
Your father wouldn't have the nerve,

303
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,080
nor do I have that kind of authority.

304
00:15:40,159 --> 00:15:43,759
He begged me to persuade you
to propose to Wushuang.

305
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,240
What?

306
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,360
Listen to me.

307
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:50,320
As things stand,

308
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:54,600
even if Chu Yunchang were to return,

309
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:58,080
do you think the two of you
could ever be together?

310
00:15:59,879 --> 00:16:02,559
Forget for a moment
that your family would be implicated.

311
00:16:02,559 --> 00:16:03,440
Do you believe

312
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:06,799
she could just abandon her family

313
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,080
just to be with you?

314
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,960
No matter how deep the love,

315
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,360
it is simply not meant to be.

316
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,159
Do not forget,

317
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:15,000
you are the only son of the Mao family.

318
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:17,559
Restoring the family name
and continuing the lineage

319
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:19,679
are responsibilities
you must carry alone.

320
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:22,320
Are you going to stay single
because of her?

321
00:16:24,399 --> 00:16:25,840
Having no heir is the greatest sin

322
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,039
against filial piety.

323
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:28,879
At this rate,

324
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:31,799
how can you face the Mao ancestors?

325
00:16:33,279 --> 00:16:33,960
The wine is here.

326
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:34,879
Thank you.

327
00:16:37,159 --> 00:16:37,960
Enjoy.

328
00:16:40,799 --> 00:16:41,440
I know

329
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:44,120
you need some time to reflect on this.

330
00:16:44,559 --> 00:16:45,399
It's just that

331
00:16:46,612 --> 00:16:49,053
the Commissioner and Ms. Wushuang

332
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,080
are both waiting for your reply.

333
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:57,120
Thank you, Director Liu.

334
00:16:57,519 --> 00:16:58,799
I have taken your words to heart.

335
00:16:59,679 --> 00:17:03,000
However, I need some time to consider it.

336
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:03,879
Naturally.

337
00:17:10,587 --> 00:17:13,862
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

338
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:16,775
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

339
00:17:17,275 --> 00:17:22,993
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

340
00:17:24,175 --> 00:17:27,495
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

341
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:30,545
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

342
00:17:31,713 --> 00:17:36,953
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

343
00:17:38,175 --> 00:17:40,568
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

344
00:17:40,568 --> 00:17:44,218
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

345
00:17:44,287 --> 00:17:47,777
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

346
00:17:47,875 --> 00:17:50,850
♪To the ends of time♪

347
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:54,225
♪The moon traces your face♪

348
00:17:54,412 --> 00:17:58,000
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

349
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:04,240
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

350
00:18:04,575 --> 00:18:07,790
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

351
00:18:08,075 --> 00:18:11,613
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

352
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:14,925
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

353
00:18:14,925 --> 00:18:18,025
♪On our way to forever♪

354
00:18:18,025 --> 00:18:21,875
♪The moon traces your face♪

355
00:18:21,875 --> 00:18:25,235
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

356
00:18:25,425 --> 00:18:31,385
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

357
00:18:32,462 --> 00:18:42,102
♪Just to be with you♪
